cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is about multi-object tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a novel method for optimizing tracklet consistency, which involves training an end-to-end tracklet search process. This suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on MOT15~17 challenge benchmarks, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM).
